QuestData.Title: Vinyl: Gnomeregan Forever
QuestData.Description:
<This pressed vinyl is surprisingly still intact. Its label says it contains the recording of a song called "Gnomeregan Forever."
You should be able to install this vinyl into the gramophone back in Rustbolt.>
